channel.desc: The Aztecs square off with the Cougars from Martin Stadium. San Diego State stomped Stony Brook 42-0 to begin the season Aug. 28. Washington State inched past Idaho 13-10 on Aug. 30. San Diego State is slated to join the Pac-12 on July 1, 2026.
